{"tid":1296659,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明報發聲明冀警尊重記者合法採訪權","createTime":"2019-07-08T12:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T14:06:59.000Z","uid":212626,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0328fedab02ba4a5793c0968a9b7cacf4bfe3b61","tid":1296659,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:22:56.000Z","msg":"大批市民昨日在反修例遊行結束後，轉往佔據旺角彌敦道一帶馬路，警方晚上11時前採取驅散行動。<br />\n<br />\n《明報》發表的聲明指出，該報記者昨晚(7日)深夜在旺角彌敦道採訪警察清場，在警察列陣前方合適距離下拍攝，一名警員揮動警棍驅趕，即使記者已穿上可供識別的黃背心，展示記者證，該名警員仍趨前驅趕。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">《明報》編輯部對記者在現場合法採訪，沒有阻礙警員工作下，遭警員揮警棍驅趕及用盾牌遮擋鏡頭，表示遺憾，並希望警方尊重記者的合法採訪權利。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2186414/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2186414%2F&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpTmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=a88d73ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2186414/</a><br />\n日月報都表示遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02a514cac84809cd4e65254b350122fa90c317d","tid":1296659,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:25:09.000Z","msg":"RTHK：記協攝及記協發聯合聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1294833/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1294833/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"3a53854932f97f6b1a3c89b641ce9c21ad388e3c","tid":1296659,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d329548bf94955ff5b82d0f02d30340873ddbc86","tid":1296659,"uid":111670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:28:48.000Z","msg":"明報又反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d7b2b9daafa54f8b35e30eceff94a888034eaa","tid":1296659,"uid":270946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:28:50.000Z"